Job Opportunity---British Embassy
The Foreign &amp; Commonwealth Office (FCO) manages Britain\'s foreign affairs. It 
aims to promote internationally the interests of the United Kingdom and to con
tribute to a strong world community. In addition to its offices in London, the
 FCO operates a network of 222 diplomatic posts around the world that employ 2
,400 UK-based staff and 8,000 local staff. 
Britain has an Embassy in Beijing, and Consulates-General in Shanghai, Guangzh
ou and Chongqing. The responsibilities of these posts include the promotion of
 trade and investment between Britain and China, the development of political,
 economic and defense ties, the provision of visa services, and the consular p
rotection of British citizens. All posts work closely with the China-Britain B
usiness Council, local British Chambers of Commerce and with the Cultural and 
Education Section, which operates independently. 
For more information about the work of the British Embassy and Consulates, ple
ase visit our website at www.britishembassy.org.cn 
British Embassy is looking for qualified staff. Please read the job requiremen
ts carefully, apply only if you meet the required criteria\'s. 
 
